article.headline: Wolf scores 22 to lead Yale to 73-66 victory over Quinnipiac

images.name: Casey Simmons with the and-1 bucket
images.caption: Casey Simmons with the and-1 bucket

article.linkText: Wolf scores 22 to lead Yale to 73-66 victory over Quinnipiac
article.story: HAMDEN, Conn. -- — Danny Wolf's 22 points helped Yale defeat Quinnipiac 73-66 on Monday night. Wolf added 12 rebounds for the Bulldogs (7-5). John Poulakidas added 12 points while shooting 4 for 9, including 2 for 6 from beyond the arc, and had five rebounds. Casey Simmons had 11 points and finished 4 of 5 from the field. Matt Balanc finished with 25 points for the Bobcats (7-3). Doug Young added 18 points and two steals for Quinnipiac. In addition, Amarri Tice finished with six points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
